          ${d.level ? d.level + ' ' : ''}${title} with a strong foundation in ${d.skills.slice(0,4).join(', ') || 'relevant skills'}.
          ${d.location ? 'Based in ' + d.location + '.' : ''}
          Seeking to contribute expertise and drive results in a high-impact role.
